                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/extra-doctrine-collections/many-to-many-setup.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Let's talk about the famous, ManyToMany relationship. We already have a <code>Genus</code> entity
and also a <code>User</code> entity. Before this tutorial, I updated the fixtures file.
It still loads genuses, but it now loads <em>two</em> groups of users:</p>
