<h3 id="doctrine-arraycollection">Doctrine ArrayCollection <a class="headerlink" href="many-to-many-setup#doctrine-arraycollection" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h3>
<p>Finally, whenever you have a Doctrine relationship where your property is an <em>array</em>
of items, so, <code>ManyToMany</code> and <code>OneToMany</code>, you need to initialize that property
in the <code>__construct()</code> method. Set <code>$this-&gt;genusScientists</code> to a <code>new ArrayCollection()</code>:</p>
