</p>
<p>Woohoo!</p>
<p><em>Now</em> it creates a <code>genus_scientist</code> table with those foreign keys. Execute the
migration:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate</div></code></pre>
<p>Guys: with about 5 lines of code, we just setup a <code>ManyToMany</code> relationship. Next
question: how do we add stuff to it? Or, read from it?</p>

    
